cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
1) cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and emotion analysis in text. 
2) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a new task and approach for emotion analysis, which involves machine learning and data-driven methods. 
3) cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses multi-task learning to perform emotion and cause extraction. 
4) cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a potential category as the paper deals with extracting information (emotion-cause pairs) from text documents. 
5) cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also possible as the paper may involve the use of neural networks for emotion and cause extraction.
